Litman - a simple reference manager.

Dependencies:
  - Ruby
  - Gtk3
  - Sqlite

  - Gems:
    - gtk3
    - bibtex-ruby
    - sqlite3

Build:
  $ gem build litman
  $ gem install --user-install litman-x.x.x.gem

Basic Usage:

Click Settings, set the directories, click update.

Opening Files:

When opening files litman seaches for <key>.pdf and <basename>.pdf.
  <key>        The key used to cite the document
  <basename>   The name of the file the entry in defined in
